Name: Fantasy Sliding Puzzle 4
About the game: Challenging sliding puzzles with various levels of difficulty, featuring epic female characters in dark fantasy environments. Relaxing background music to match the fantasy theme and mood. Features: - 12 different puzzles to solve - 3 levels of difficulty: 3x3, 4x4 and 5x5 - Timer, to see how long it takes to solve a puzzle - Gallery where you can view all the puzzle images you have solved. Be among the fastest puzzle solvers to achieve a top spot in our Leaderboards and unlock various achievements.
